      "instruction": "<p>Boil a kettle</p><p>Once the chicken has browned, add a splash of<strong> cold water </strong>and cook, covered for 10-12 min or until the chicken is cooked through (no pink meat!)</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
