      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the chicken is cooking, add your <strong>wholewheat noodles</strong> to a pot and cover them with <strong>boiled water</strong> until they're fully submerged</p><p>Bring to the boil over a high heat and cook for 5-7 min or until tender with a slight bite, then drain and set aside in a bowl and reserve the pot for later</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1692624861361-x200.jpg",
