      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Wash your <strong>spring greens </strong>then pat it dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Rip the leaves off your <strong>spring greens</strong>, discard the tough stalks, then layer the leaves over each other, roll them up and slice into thin strips</p><p>Trim, then slice your <strong>spring onion[s]</strong> finely</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1692624864475-x200.jpg",
